\prod_{i=1}^{\infty}\left(1-\frac{2}{(i+1)(i+2)}\right)^2=\prod_{i=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{i(i+3)}{(i+1)(i+2)}\right)^2=\prod_{i=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{i+3}{i+2}\right)^2=\frac{1}{3^2}
